['All of the data provided by the TFMData service is structured XML data. Appendix B describes in detail the elements and types of all TFMData messages in a tabular form and includes constraints, ranges, and acceptable values. The TFMData schema is published and available via the NAS Service Registry and Repository (NSRR). The TFMData Service business functions International Data and Terminal Data are dependent on the FIXM Core v3.0 Schemas and FIXM US Extension v3.1 Schemas which are not captured in Appendix B. Full documentation on FIXM Core v3.0 Schemas and the FIXM US Extension v3.1 Schemas extension can be found at ', '.', 'TFMData is documented in the FAA Data Registry (FDR) under the namespace urn:us:gov:dot:faa:atm:tfm.']
